        },
        {
            "title": "川普團隊警告稱 政府停擺持續將導致更多航班延誤",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Sean Duffy\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tGNLZLZ12Fbxxh60FDE0iQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/eae759ff9c9dca0522f451935e57a224\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Sean Duffy</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國交通部長肖恩·達菲警告稱，隨著政府關門進入第四周，美國各地的航班運行將繼續受到干擾。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我無法向你保證你的航班會准點，也無法向你保證你的航班不會被取消，」他周四向記者表示。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">目前，全美逾1.3萬名空中交通管制員和5萬名運輸安全管理局（TSA）工作人員被迫在政府停擺期間無薪工作。以往政府關門期間，這往往導致員工請病假人數上升 —— 這一趨勢似乎在本次停擺中再次出現。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"肖恩·達菲攝影師：Michael Nagle/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XdFkPybws3nYf2pq9_mz3w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e780d8f1eeee60a06f1830a54cc9a908\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">肖恩·達菲攝影師：Michael Nagle/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">達菲表示，通常情況下，由空管人員短缺造成的航班延誤比例約5%，但自政府關門以來，這一比例已升至50%以上。達拉斯、芝加哥、納什維爾以及華盛頓特區周邊等全美多個機場均已報告出現因人手不足而引發的航班中斷。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-92377f2f-3fbf-3cc4-b716-9990c5d1bd79-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Team Warns of More Flight Delays If US Shutdown Continues</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%9C%98%E9%9A%8A%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E7%A8%B1-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%81%9C%E6%93%BA%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%B0%87%E5%B0%8E%E8%87%B4%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E5%BB%B6%E8%AA%A4-161010221.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 01:20:46",
