            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "川普再對幣圈伸出橄欖枝 赦免幣安創始人趙長鵬",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 因未能防止洗錢而被判入獄服刑的幣安聯合創始人<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:趙長鵬;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/趙長鵬\">趙長鵬</a>獲得美國總統川普的赦免。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白宮發言人萊維特表示，「川普總統行使憲法賦予的權力赦免趙先生，他是在拜登政府對加密貨幣發動戰爭期間被起訴的」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次赦免是白宮對加密貨幣企業家的最新寬宥舉措，凸顯川普政府積極將自己定位為該行業的朋友。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">趙長鵬於2024年服刑四個月，此前他承認未能在幣安落實有效的反洗錢措施。這項認罪協議是他與美國政府達成的一攬子和解的一部分，其中包括幣安支付43億美元的罰款。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a14f12e4-c3e4-3077-aff5-94887d814fba-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：[深度] 想拿到川普簽署的特赦令？先準備100萬美元的律師費用</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">趙長鵬在2023年認罪協議中同意辭去幣安執行長職務，但得以保留公司控股權。自川普贏得總統選舉以來，幣安估值迅速飆升。據彭博億萬富翁指數，趙長鵬目前淨資產達545億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Binance Founder Zhao Pardoned by Trump in Latest Crypto Clemency</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Ava Benny-Morrison、Sabrina Willmer.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%86%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%B9%A3%E5%9C%88%E4%BC%B8%E5%87%BA%E6%A9%84%E6%AC%96%E6%9E%9D-%E8%B5%A6%E5%85%8D%E5%B9%A3%E5%AE%89%E5%89%B5%E5%A7%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B6%99%E9%95%B7%E9%B5%AC-155406473.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 01:20:47",
