            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "私募巨頭KKR創始人反駁市場憂慮 稱私人信貸不具系統性風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> KKR &amp; Co.聯合創始人Henry Kravis反駁了關於Tricolor Holdings和First Brands Group的危機可能預示私人信貸領域將出現更廣泛問題的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「大家都在說，天哪，私人信貸要出問題了，」Kravis周四在柏林全球對話大會（Berlin Global Dialog）接受彭博記者Francine Lacqua採訪時表示。雖然美國在過去幾周出現「兩起大型破產案」，但「其中沒有一分錢來自私人信貸」。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5ccc967f-eb86-3f9c-a056-42e672c6f80d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">銀行與私人信貸領域的高管在這兩起破產事件後互相指責，雙方都宣稱自身在應對經濟下行時處於更有利的位置。私人信貸行業規模在金融危機後急劇膨脹，部分原因在於政府加強了對商業銀行的監管並降低風險。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：戴蒙「蟑螂」說引發私人信貸業反擊 稱銀行盡職調查不嚴謹才是關鍵</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kravis指出，由於像KKR這樣的投資公司並不吸收存款，因此私人信貸作為一種資產類別不會帶來系統性風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我擔心的是那些沒有駕照卻想開車的機構，他們決定涉足私人信貸，但既不會操作，也沒通過任何考核，」他說。「他們會遇到問題嗎？有可能。但我不認為是系統性的。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題KKR Co-Founder Kravis Sees No Systemic Risk in Private Credit</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%81%E5%8B%9F%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%ADkkr%E5%89%B5%E5%A7%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%8D%E9%A7%81%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%86%82%E6%85%AE-%E7%A8%B1%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%A1%E8%B2%B8%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%B7%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E6%80%A7%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-131020629.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-23 22:05:51",
