            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全球對沖基金資產規模觸及5萬億美元大關 單季淨流入創07年以來新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"HFR\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"588\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ia5G.MJI_uVtcFBnWd5T8Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4ODtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4515be9ad5e1a39be90ff4ce14910484\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">HFR</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 全球<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:對沖基金;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/對沖基金\">對沖基金</a>行業資產規模飆升至創紀錄的5萬億美元，得益於投資者加碼另類資產以及基金所取得的穩健回報。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據Hedge Fund Research Inc.(HFR)周四發布的數據，在截至9月的三個月內，對沖基金實現近340億美元的淨流入，為2007年全球金融危機前以來單季最高。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資表現亦推升了資產規模：各類策略的季度平均總回報為5.4%，期內股票和宏觀對沖基金策略漲幅居前。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"588\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4pyB1yBdfEFN.E3YJqXoUA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4ODtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/070f51a0ad80b976268e3c35702d0420\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在地緣政治緊張、美國總統唐納德·川普在一系列問題上的舉措令今年市場波動加劇之際，投資者日益尋求對沖基金提供非相關性的回報。對沖基金受益於美股走強，以及關稅相關因素推動的債券和外匯市場波動。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-82ed54d3-d17a-3078-9a5b-5668e08b549f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們在尋找當下能夠分散風險的資產，不會被經濟環境不同部分的熱炒所左右，並且能以非相關的方式產生超額收益(alpha) —— 在環境好時如此，在狀況不佳時，尤其也要能夠保持非相關性，」Man Group Plc旗下External Alpha的首席投資官Adam Singleton周三在倫敦彭博對沖基金論壇的一場討論中表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">HFR稱，第三季度新增淨資金再次主要流向業內最大型的公司，幾乎全部配置給管理規模超過50億美元的機構。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">HFR還表示，加密貨幣對沖基金在第三季度錄得穩健的兩位數漲幅，扭轉了2025年年初的明顯虧損，將年迄今回報推升至6.7%。該機構指出，交易活動加速、加密貨幣投資、地緣政治風險回落、押注降息，以及人工智能投資與基礎設施的空前激增，都是近期對沖基金行業成長的推動因素。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Hedge Fund Assets Hit $5 Trillion With Most Inflows Since 2007</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%B0%8D%E6%B2%96%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E8%A7%B8%E5%8F%8A5%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%97%9C-%E5%96%AE%E5%AD%A3%E6%B7%A8%E6%B5%81%E5%85%A5%E5%89%B507%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-120820124.html",
